name: Eternal Night (1 of 1)
description:
"The night is ours,
Stuck in time.
A place we exist forever,
A place we are always alive.

Eternal is the universe,
& Dark is the night.
But we are here always,
Living on in the moons extravagant light."
- SolarKittyn
